### ============================================================
### TIME-TRAVELER QUICK START
### Benjamin's Loan Simulation REST API
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================================
### 1. LOGIN AS ADMIN (get JWT token)
### ============================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "jaytechwavesolutions@gmail.com",
  "password": "Michira._2000"
}

> {%
    const raw = response.headers.valueOf("Set-Cookie");
    if (raw) {
        const match = raw.match(/XSRF-TOKEN=([^;]+)/);
        if (match) client.global.set("csrf_token", match[1]);
        const s = raw.match(/SACCO_SESSION=([^;]+)/);
        if (s) client.global.set("admin_cookie", "SACCO_SESSION=" + s[1]);
    }
    // For JWT-based auth (if using stateless API):
    if (response.body && response.body.token) {
        client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token);
    }
%}

### ============================================================
### 2. CHECK INITIAL TIME-TRAVEL STATUS
### ============================================================
### Should show Week 0, Virtual Date = 2022-10-06, Progress = 0%

GET {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 3. RESET SIMULATION (ensure clean state)
### ============================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 4. ADVANCE TIME BY 4 WEEKS
### ============================================================
### Virtual Date should advance to ~2022-11-03 (4 weeks forward)

POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/advance?weeks=4
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 5. CHECK STATUS AGAIN
### ============================================================
### Should now show Week 4, Virtual Date = 2022-11-03, Progress ≈ 2.3%

GET {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 6. CHECK PROGRESS PERCENTAGE
### ============================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 7. ADVANCE LARGE JUMP (26 weeks = ~6 months virtual)
### ============================================================
### This should get us to ~May 2023 (midway through Loan 1)

POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/advance?weeks=26
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 8. QUERY BENJAMIN'S LOAN STATUS AT VIRTUAL DATE
### ============================================================
### This endpoint should be implemented to query loan state
### at the current virtual date (requires additional endpoint)

GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/search?memberNumber=BVL-2022-000001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 9. CHECK LOAN SCHEDULE AT CURRENT VIRTUAL TIME
### ============================================================
### Shows which installments are DUE, PENDING, PAID, OVERDUE

GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/schedule?memberNumber=BVL-2022-000001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 10. BIG JUMP: Advance to Loan 2 Refinance Date (May 30, 2024)
### ============================================================
### From Week 4 → ~Week 61 (57 weeks forward = ~10 months virtual)

POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/advance?weeks=57
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 11. VERIFY REFINANCE IS NOW ELIGIBLE
### ============================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/BVL-2022-000001/refinance-eligibility
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 12. JUMP TO LOAN 3 RESTRUCTURE DATE (Oct 10, 2024)
### ============================================================
### Advance another 18 weeks from current position

POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/advance?weeks=18
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 13. VERIFY RESTRUCTURE IS ELIGIBLE
### ============================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/BVL-2022-000001/restructure-eligibility
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 14. JUMP TO NEAR END OF SIMULATION (Aug 2025)
### ============================================================
### Advance remaining weeks to ~85% complete

POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/advance?weeks=45
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 15. FINAL STATUS CHECK (should be near 100%)
### ============================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 16. VERIFY ALL LOANS MARKED PAID
### ============================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/search?memberNumber=BVL-2022-000001&status=PAID
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### 17. RESET AND START OVER
### ============================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### AUTOMATED TEST SEQUENCE
### ============================================================
### Copy/paste sequence for continuous testing:
### 1. Reset to start
### 2. Loop: Advance 4 weeks
### 3. Verify schedule state
### 4. Repeat until complete

### Reset
POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### Week 4
POST {{baseUrl}}/time-travel/advance?weeks=4
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### Check Schedule
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/schedule?memberNumber=BVL-2022-000001
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Cookie: {{admin_cookie}}

### ============================================================
### NOTES
### ============================================================
###
### - Replace {{admin_token}} with actual JWT token from login response
### - Replace {{admin_cookie}} with actual XSRF + SESSION cookies
###
### - Automatic cron job runs every 6 hours and advances 1 week
###   If you see status unchanged after 6 hours, check backend logs
###
### - Virtual date calculation: 2022-10-06 + (weeks * 7 days)
###   Week 0 = 2022-10-06
###   Week 1 = 2022-10-13
###   Week 52 = 2023-10-05
###   Week 104 = 2024-10-04
###   Week 170 = 2025-08-28 (end)
###
### - To disable automatic progression, comment out @Scheduled in TimeTravelerService
### - Simulation halts automatically when reaching Aug 28, 2025
###
### ============================================================

